    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(Dolphin Polypeptide-1 Hexapeptide-40) s a single chain recombinant peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sr-Dolphin Polypeptide-1 and Hexapeptide-40. The fusion peptide contains 196 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
